EN: When I opened the curtains, the dawn had already filled the room.

ZH: 看！第一缕曙光正在东方升起。
EN: Look! The first ray of dawn is rising in the east.

ZH: 这幅画描绘了一幅美丽的曙光背景。
EN: This painting depicts a beautiful sunrise background.

ZH: 每天早晨看到曙光会让我心情愉悦。
EN: Seeing the dawn every morning makes me feel joyful.

ZH: 曙光是一切开始的象征。
EN: Dawn is a symbol of new beginnings.

ZH: 当曙光出现时，夜幕终将散去。
EN: When dawn appears, the night will finally dissipate.

