EN: Waiting for the dawn by the riverside is a peaceful and beautiful experience.

ZH: 曙光的出现为这个城市带来了勃勃生机。
EN: The appearance of dawn brings vitality to this city.

ZH: 高山之巅是眺望曙光的绝佳位置。
EN: The summit of the mountain is an excellent spot to view the dawn.

ZH: 每个新的曙光都代表着新的机遇。
EN: Every new dawn represents new opportunities.

ZH: 当曙光破晓时，小鸟开始歌唱。
EN: When dawn breaks, the birds start singing.

